info.description: This works, describe the pic you want or send an imgur link in the comments. Read the help sections for help. Credits go to >Project Sekai: Colorful Stage<. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
info.additionalInfo: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Won't work for tablets/iPads or phones. The style not appearing or downloading bug is an issue with the extension, not the style. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi. French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. A disclaimer: all the translations I make are just Google translated, I ain't no multilingual savant, so if there are any readers who are proficient in the languages above, please do tell me where I've messed up. 13 May 2023 - Released.
